      "y": 0,
      "name": "Frame",
      "clip": true,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 600,
      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
      "layout": "none"
    },
    {
      "type": "prompt",
      "id": "F2W6N",
      "x": -270,
      "y": 0,
      "model": "claude-4.5-sonnet",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 219,
      "content": "Generate a responsive web landing page in \"Frame\" for the DonatJS fundraising platform using a clean, story-driven design heavily inspired by GoFundMe. Use a crisp white background with soft gray borders and a vibrant Kelly Green for primary call-to-action buttons and progress bars to build trust and encourage giving. The layout should start with a minimalist navigation bar containing the DonatJS logo, a search input, and clear \"Log In\" and \"Sign Up\" buttons. Below the nav, create a welcoming hero section featuring a large, inspiring community photo, a headline about transparent solidarity, and a prominent \"Start a Campaign\" button. The main content area must feature a responsive grid displaying active fundraising campaigns as large, image-heavy cards. Each campaign card should prioritize a high-quality cover photo, followed by the campaign title, the organizer's name, a thick and highly visible green progress bar showing total funds raised versus the target, and a small text indicator for the deadline. Ensure the typography uses a friendly, highly legible sans-serif font like Montserrat or Proxima Nova to maximize readability and emotional connection."
    },
